Siya ay isang mabuting tao.

37
00:05:22.132 --> 00:05:24.085
Mahal ko si Ja Yeong.

38
00:05:30.840 --> 00:05:32.873
At least sana nagsinungaling ka

39
00:05:33.627 --> 00:05:35.713
at sinabing wala lang.

40
00:05:37.029 --> 00:05:39.902
At least nagsinungaling ka

41
00:05:39.902 --> 00:05:43.362
at sinabi na wala silang ibig sabihin
para sa isa't isa.

42
