92
00:13:11.413 --> 00:13:12.931
Oscar.

93
00:13:13.925 --> 00:13:15.725
Oscar?

94
00:13:17.040 --> 00:13:18.815
Napakaganda ng tunog.

95
00:13:22.026 --> 00:13:24.851
<i>Mukhang lumipas na ang alabok ng tagsibol,</i>

96
00:13:24.851 --> 00:13:27.328
<i>pero lately marami sa inyo ang nagrereklamo</i>

97
00:13:27.328 --> 00:13:30.840
