Ikaw din, Do Hyun.

151
00:19:16.100 --> 00:19:17.939
<i>Magkita tayo mamaya.</i>

152
00:19:17.939 --> 00:19:19.552
Oo.

153
00:19:33.448 --> 00:19:35.733
