219
00:24:57.102 --> 00:25:00.730
at lahat ay sasabog na parang galit.

220
00:25:01.944 --> 00:25:04.644
Maaari mo bang i-summarize ang lahat ng iyon...

221
00:25:05.471 --> 00:25:08.288
parang "Miss niya na siya"?

222
00:25:08.288 --> 00:25:09.543
[Nakakaramdam siya ng kalungkutan para sa kanya.]

223
00:25:09.543 --> 00:25:11.788
Sa tingin ko ito ay magiging paghihirap.

224
00:25:14.756 --> 00:25:16.711
may tao ba

225
00:25:16.711 --> 00:25:19.363
Sino ang mahal mo, Hye On?

226
00:25:23.403 --> 00:25:24.800
Sa edad mo?

227
00:25:24.800 --> 00:25:27.435
May taong magpapahirap sa kanya?

228
00:25:27.435 --> 00:25:30.426
At most, mami-miss ko lang siya.

229
00:25:30.426 --> 00:25:31.743
Hindi, siyempre hindi.

230
00:25:31.743 --> 00:25:35.625
Siguro naging maganda ang pagmamahal na gusto ko.

231
00:25:35.625 --> 00:25:37.775
O baka naman

232
00:25:37.775 --> 00:25:39.593
hindi niya ito ginusto,

233
00:25:39.593 --> 00:25:42.575
dahil hindi man lang niya namalayan
na iyon ay pag-ibig.

234
00:25:42.575 --> 00:25:43.720
Teka.

235
00:25:43.720 --> 00:25:46.600
Personal story mo yan ha?

236
00:25:46.600 --> 00:25:48.065
Paano kung ito nga?

237
00:25:48.065 --> 00:25:50.006
Sa tingin mo ba napaka-inosente mo?

238
00:25:50.540 --> 00:25:52.644
inosente?

239
00:25:52.644 --> 00:25:55.300
naging tanga lang ako.

240
00:25:55.300 --> 00:25:57.773
<i>Ang pagka-miss sa isang tao ay isang damdamin,</i>

241
00:25:58.512 --> 00:26:01.819
<i>ngunit sa ngayon
kung saan ito ay nagiging pagdurusa,</i>

242
00:26:02.886 --> 00:26:05.039
<i>nagsisimula itong masaktan.</i>

243
00:26:07.772 --> 00:26:10.972
<i>Nakakakuha ito sa ilalim ng iyong balat, nakakairita ka</i>

244
00:26:10.972 --> 00:26:13.859
<i>at saka masakit talaga.</i>

245
00:26:13.859 --> 00:26:14.960
Oo?

246
00:26:14.960 --> 00:26:17.620
Oo. Hindi mo ba naramdaman iyon?

247
00:26:17.620 --> 00:26:19.642
Hindi, huwag mo nang itanong.

248
00:26:19.642 --> 00:26:21.342
Napaka-boring ng buhay mo, hindi ba?

249
00:26:21.342 --> 00:26:23.080
Wag mo nang itanong.

250
00:26:29.659 --> 00:26:32.059
<i>Nakitulog ako kay Beom Jun.</i>

251
00:26:38.392 --> 00:26:40.260
<i>Pasensya na.</i>

252
00:26:41.926 --> 00:26:43.732
Well, paalam.

253
00:26:45.451 --> 00:26:47.277
Okay, handa na kami.

254
00:26:47.277 --> 00:26:50.303
Nakakaapekto ito sa aking reputasyon, gawin natin ito ng tama.

255
00:26:51.126 --> 00:26:52.706
Naiintindihan?

256
00:26:58.589 --> 00:26:59.989
yun?

257
00:27:02.653 --> 00:27:03.860
anong nangyayari?

258
00:27:03.860 --> 00:27:05.755
Nakikinig ka ba sa akin?

259
00:27:06.839 --> 00:27:08.445
Panginoon...

260
00:27:12.554 --> 00:27:14.553
Hindi ko akalain na magagawa ko ito.

261
00:27:17.061 --> 00:27:18.461
yun?

262
00:27:20.556 --> 00:27:23.362
Kaya lang wala na sa mga ito ang mahalaga.

263
00:27:30.366 --> 00:27:33.796
Ja Yeong, umalis ako sa bahay.

264
00:27:34.353 --> 00:27:35.753
yun?

265
00:27:37.300 --> 00:27:38.346
Oh.

266
00:27:38.346 --> 00:27:40.614
Hahayaan mo akong manatili dito, tama?

267
00:27:53.739 --> 00:27:58.272
Nakita kita kahapon, pero natutuwa akong makita kang muli, Bom.

268
00:27:59.631 --> 00:28:02.544
Well... Jin Ho,

269
00:28:02.544 --> 00:28:06.484
May meeting ako sa travel agency.

270
00:28:07.800 --> 00:28:10.154
babalik ako agad.

271
00:28:10.154 --> 00:28:11.558
Gawin ang iyong sarili sa bahay.

272
00:28:11.558 --> 00:28:14.531
Aalagaan ko siya ng mabuti, take your time.

273
00:28:15.913 --> 00:28:18.066
O pwede kitang ihatid.

274
00:28:19.080 --> 00:28:22.466
Sabi nila uulan daw,
pero maganda ang panahon.

275
00:28:23.926 --> 00:28:24.951
Ja Yeong,

276
00:28:24.951 --> 00:28:28.898
paano kung mamasyal tayo
pagkatapos ng meeting?

277
00:28:36.715 --> 00:28:37.920
Anong nangyari dito?

278
00:28:37.920 --> 00:28:39.808
Yung side mirror?

279
00:28:40.996 --> 00:28:44.040
Kaya kong ayusin, madali lang.

280
00:28:44.610 --> 00:28:46.890
ang aking hipag

281
00:28:46.890 --> 00:28:48.956
Medyo ligaw.

282
00:28:50.623 --> 00:28:53.029
Maaaring ayusin ang mga bagay na tulad nito,

283
00:28:54.170 --> 00:28:57.116
ngunit ang puso ng mga tao ay hindi, tama?

284
00:28:57.116 --> 00:28:59.790
Hindi ito isang bagay na madali mong ayusin.

285
00:28:59.790 --> 00:29:01.756
Sige.

286
00:29:19.451 --> 00:29:21.464
At ang iyong anak na babae?

287
00:29:24.150 --> 00:29:26.270
Ano ang sinabi niya?

288
00:29:30.940 --> 00:29:32.546
Jin Ho,

289
00:29:33.093 --> 00:29:35.426
okay ka lang ba talaga?

290
00:29:36.863 --> 00:29:38.976
ayos lang ako.

291
00:30:25.174 --> 00:30:27.105
Parang normal ang lahat.

292
00:30:27.105 --> 00:30:29.015
Magkita-kita tayo sa iyong susunod na appointment.

293
00:30:29.015 --> 00:30:31.345
- Salamat.
- Alagaan ang iyong sarili.

294
00:30:41.551 --> 00:30:43.342
Wala naman akong pasyente hanggang singko diba?

295
00:30:43.342 --> 00:30:45.824
- Magpapahinga ako ng 30 minuto.
- Teka.

296
00:30:45.824 --> 00:30:48.037
May dumating para makita ka.

297
00:31:07.455 --> 00:31:10.588
Paumanhin sa paglitaw nang wala saan.

298
00:31:13.812 --> 00:31:16.256
Sa totoo lang, wala man lang akong number mo.

299
00:31:16.256 --> 00:31:18.288
Balita ko dito ka lang nagtatrabaho.

300
00:31:18.288 --> 00:31:20.208
Pinadala ka ba ng tatay ko?

301
00:31:22.274 --> 00:31:24.020
Hindi.

302
00:31:26.289 --> 00:31:27.819
Dumating ako ng mag-isa.

303
00:31:27.819 --> 00:31:29.942
Hindi ka ba nahihiya?

304
00:31:32.463 --> 00:31:35.959
Dapat ba akong ikahiya dito?

305
00:31:35.959 --> 00:31:38.266
Hindi?

306
00:31:38.266 --> 00:31:41.092
At least sa ganitong sitwasyon...

307
00:31:42.852 --> 00:31:45.252
Alam kong ikakahiya ako nito.

308
00:31:50.326 --> 00:31:52.319
Kailan dapat

309
00:31:53.079 --> 00:31:55.626
tumigil ka sa kahihiyan?

310
00:32:02.170 --> 00:32:04.170
Kami ni Jin Ho

311
00:32:04.644 --> 00:32:07.443
makakatapos tayo balang araw,

312
00:32:07.443 --> 00:32:10.540
Ngunit kung mangyari iyon, ito ay magiging isang bagay sa pagitan niya at sa akin,

313
00:32:10.540 --> 00:32:12.953
hindi isang bagay mula sa kanyang pamilya.

314
00:32:15.552 --> 00:32:18.418
Ano ba talaga ang gusto mong sabihin?

315
00:32:19.703 --> 00:32:22.565
gusto ko lang.

316
00:32:22.565 --> 00:32:24.535
Hindi ko sinusubukan na maging pamilya ng sinuman.

317
00:32:24.535 --> 00:32:27.372
ni paglalaruan ang pagiging ina,

318
00:32:27.372 --> 00:32:30.265
kaya naisip ko na walang kwenta.

319
00:32:33.085 --> 00:32:36.191
- AT?
- Pero sino ako...

320
00:32:37.732 --> 00:32:40.532
at kung ano ang nararamdaman namin ng tatay mo...

321
00:32:42.932 --> 00:32:46.923
malamang
Walang pakialam ang pamilya mo, di ba?

322
00:32:52.159 --> 00:32:54.766
Napagtanto ko na naging makasarili ako.

323
00:32:58.843 --> 00:33:00.909
kararating ko lang...

324
00:33:02.529 --> 00:33:04.762
para sabihin sayo na sorry.

325
00:34:17.593 --> 00:34:19.083
<i>Honey.</i>

326
00:34:19.083 --> 00:34:20.773
<i>Oo?</i>

327
00:34:20.773 --> 00:34:22.479
<i>Pasensya na.</i>

328
00:34:23.251 --> 00:34:25.064
<i>Bakit?</i>

329
00:34:27.265 --> 00:34:28.897
<i>Para sa lahat.</i>

330
00:34:29.638 --> 00:34:31.955
<i>Sumusulong ka.</i>

331
00:34:31.955 --> 00:34:34.415
<i>Magiging maayos ang lahat.</i>

332
00:34:35.708 --> 00:34:37.105
<i>Maghintay sandali,</i>

333
00:34:37.105 --> 00:34:39.811
<i>may nasusunog ba?</i>

334
00:34:40.461 --> 00:34:43.268
<i>Ang sarsa!</i>

335
00:34:45.807 --> 00:34:48.347
<i>Sus, kailangan kong gawin itong muli.</i>

336
00:34:48.347 --> 00:34:50.667
<i>Darating sila anumang oras.</i>

337
00:35:19.363 --> 00:35:23.600
<i>Hindi ko alam kung magse-celebrate
anniversary ng kasal namin

338
00:35:23.600 --> 00:35:25.923
<i>numero 35</i>

339
00:35:25.923 --> 00:35:28.129
<i>o humingi ng tawad.</i>

340
00:35:29.047 --> 00:35:30.634
<i>Nagpasya ako</i>

341
00:35:31.261 --> 00:35:33.334
<i>sabihin lang salamat.</i>

342
00:35:36.045 --> 00:35:37.995
<i>Ang parehong uri ng ngiti</i>

343
00:35:37.995 --> 00:35:40.672
<i>na lagi mong ibinibigay sa akin kapag nakatingin ka sa akin</i>

344
00:35:40.672 --> 00:35:44.628
<i>37 taon na ang nakalipas.</i>

345
00:35:45.534 --> 00:35:49.592
<i>Ang walang lasa ng pagkain mo.</i>

346
00:35:50.143 --> 00:35:54.203
<i>Ang malamyang mga ingay na ginagawa mo kapag gumagalaw ka.</i>

347
00:35:55.643 --> 00:35:58.595
<i>Ang masasamang biro na sinasabi mo</i>

348
00:35:58.595 --> 00:36:01.228
<i>at iyong tinatawanan mong mag-isa.</i>

349
00:36:02.933 --> 00:36:04.439
<i>ako</i>

350
00:36:05.373 --> 00:36:07.399
<i>Gustung-gusto ko ang lahat ng iyon.</i>

351
00:36:09.153 --> 00:36:10.712
<i>Mahal,</i>

352
00:36:11.259 --> 00:36:12.976
<i>ngayon,</i>

353
00:36:12.976 --> 00:36:15.509
<i>sa aming ika-35 anibersaryo...</i>

354
00:36:17.696 --> 00:36:18.826
<i>Tatay!</i>

355
00:36:18.826 --> 00:36:20.489
<i>Kailangan mo ba ng tulong?</i>

356
00:36:20.489 --> 00:36:23.382
<i>Sa tamang panahon. Hugasan ito para sa akin.</i>

357
00:37:10.975 --> 00:37:15.568
Dapat alam ko kung paano mo ako makikita.

358
00:37:17.108 --> 00:37:19.088
Naging pabaya ako.

359
00:37:21.747 --> 00:37:24.594
At least, nagtagal.

360
00:37:25.901 --> 00:37:27.901
Hindi ang oras ko...

361
00:37:30.901 --> 00:37:33.847
sa iyo at sa iyong pamilya.

362
00:37:42.075 --> 00:37:45.181
<i>Ako ang pinaka-makasarili...</i>

363
00:37:47.696 --> 00:37:49.849
<i>ngunit patuloy akong sumisigaw...</i>

364
00:37:51.949 --> 00:37:54.866
<i>na ako ang nagdusa at nasaktan.</i>

365
00:37:54.866 --> 00:37:57.095
<i>Hindi ka ba nahihiya?</i>

366
00:37:59.249 --> 00:38:01.568
<i>Ako ang taong iyon.</i>

367
00:38:03.788 --> 00:38:06.055
<i>Ako ang batang iyon.</i>

368
00:38:08.489 --> 00:38:10.225
<i>Paano ko masisisi ang sinuman</i>

369
00:38:10.225 --> 00:38:12.365
<i>o tawagin siyang duwag?</i>

370
00:38:16.112 --> 00:38:18.045
<i>Seo Jun Kyung...</i>

371
00:38:19.665 --> 00:38:23.258
<i>nakakaawa ka.</i>

372
00:38:50.810 --> 00:38:52.683
honey.

373
00:39:08.041 --> 00:39:09.654
Jun Kyung?

374
00:39:10.715 --> 00:39:12.613
Nabasa ka ba sa ulan?

375
00:39:12.613 --> 00:39:15.207
Kung wala kang payong, dapat tumawag ka.

376
00:39:15.207 --> 00:39:17.199
Gusto kong mabasa.

377
00:39:17.199 --> 00:39:18.839
Dahil?

378
00:39:49.109 --> 00:39:50.855
Yoon Sol.

379
00:39:51.802 --> 00:39:53.895
Hoy Yoon Sol!

380
00:39:57.266 --> 00:39:59.406
Hindi ko kayang makipaghiwalay sayo.

381
00:39:59.406 --> 00:40:01.420
Napag-usapan na natin ito.

382
00:40:01.420 --> 00:40:03.670
- Natapos mo, hindi ako.
-Seo Jun Seo!

383
00:40:03.670 --> 00:40:05.210
Hey.

384
00:40:11.465 --> 00:40:13.089
Mag-usap tayo sa labas.

385
00:40:13.089 --> 00:40:16.136
- Wala akong masabi.
- Kailangan kong sabihin sa iyo!

386
00:40:16.136 --> 00:40:17.742
Hoy!

387
00:40:18.716 --> 00:40:20.233
Wala daw siyang masabi.

388
00:40:20.233 --> 00:40:21.928
Sino ka ba?

389
00:40:21.928 --> 00:40:24.080
Kung tapos na, kumilos nang naaayon.

390
00:40:24.080 --> 00:40:25.277
Huwag masyadong pathetic.

391
00:40:25.277 --> 00:40:27.170
Hoy tumigil ka din.

392
00:40:29.348 --> 00:40:31.594
piraso ng tae.

393
00:40:32.624 --> 00:40:35.075
- Itong sumpain...
- Tumigil ka!

394
00:40:35.075 --> 00:40:37.070
Halika dito!

395
00:40:37.070 --> 00:40:39.543
- Idiot ka!
- Saktan mo ako kung kaya mo.

396
00:40:39.543 --> 00:40:41.069
- Papatayin kita.
- Bitawan mo ako!

397
00:40:41.069 --> 00:40:43.047
- Tumawag ng pulis!
- Halika!

398
00:40:43.047 --> 00:40:45.075
Ang lakas ng loob mo!

399
00:40:46.068 --> 00:40:47.710
Kinagat ako nito!

400
00:40:47.710 --> 00:40:49.891
Anong kalokohan ang ginagawa mo?

401
00:40:52.121 --> 00:40:54.715
- Ano ang gagawin natin?
- Ayos lang ako.

402
00:40:54.715 --> 00:40:57.028
Hindi ba dapat pumunta ka sa ospital?

403
00:40:57.028 --> 00:40:58.378
Hindi naman ganoon kaseryoso.

404
00:40:58.378 --> 00:41:01.074
- Magandang langit.
- Iyan ay dapat na napakasakit.

405
00:41:12.313 --> 00:41:14.247
Anong ginagawa mo dito?

406
00:41:17.447 --> 00:41:19.347
Anong nangyari sa mukha mo?

407
00:41:21.034 --> 00:41:23.397
Dapat kang magmakaawa sa guro

408
00:41:23.397 --> 00:41:26.067
Nawa'y bigyan kita ng isa pang pagkakataon.

409
00:41:26.067 --> 00:41:30.660
Sino ba naman ang sisira ng pagkakataong ganyan?
dahil lang iniwan nila ito?

410
00:41:31.687 --> 00:41:34.307
Tapos na ba ang buhay mo? Oh talaga?

411
00:41:34.927 --> 00:41:38.424
Bakit ka pumunta at hinayaan kang saktan ka niya ng ganyan?

412
00:41:38.424 --> 00:41:40.287
Tingnan mo mukha ko.

413
00:41:40.287 --> 00:41:42.757
Ano sa tingin mo ang hitsura niya?

414
00:41:42.757 --> 00:41:45.450
Nawasak ito.

415
00:41:46.537 --> 00:41:47.937
AT?

416
00:41:48.893 --> 00:41:50.864
Mas maganda ba ang pakiramdam mo ngayon?

417
00:41:54.413 --> 00:41:55.813
Hindi.

418
00:41:56.673 --> 00:41:58.399
nakakakilabot ang pakiramdam ko.

419
00:42:04.574 --> 00:42:06.353
Masakit yun.

420
00:42:08.754 --> 00:42:10.353
Oo?

421
00:42:14.267 --> 00:42:16.127
Gaano kalungkot.

422
00:42:31.665 --> 00:42:33.471
Bakit ka umiiyak?

423
00:42:35.192 --> 00:42:38.051
- Dahil?
- Nalulungkot din ako.

424
00:42:39.372 --> 00:42:41.171
Ikaw? Dahil?

425
00:42:44.525 --> 00:42:47.285
Dahil mahal kita.

426
00:42:52.442 --> 00:42:55.461
Na gusto ko ang isang taong tanga at nakakaawa...

427
00:42:57.132 --> 00:43:00.456
Nalulungkot ako!

428
00:43:07.620 --> 00:43:09.134
yun?

429
00:43:17.838 --> 00:43:19.238
Yo...

430
00:43:20.871 --> 00:43:23.011
mahal kita.

431
00:44:31.553 --> 00:44:33.934
<i>May lagnat ka.</i>

432
00:44:33.934 --> 00:44:37.813
<i>Gumawa ako ng oatmeal cream.
Kumain at inumin ang iyong mga gamot.</i>

433
00:44:57.052 --> 00:44:59.245
Bakit hindi ka kumakain?

434
00:45:06.779 --> 00:45:08.725
Magpapalamig ito.

435
00:45:13.997 --> 00:45:15.570
nanay...

436
00:45:18.084 --> 00:45:20.750
Sa tingin ko ako ang pinakamasama.

437
00:45:25.202 --> 00:45:27.261
Nakakaawa...

438
00:45:29.222 --> 00:45:32.054
duwag, nakakakilabot.

439
00:45:35.826 --> 00:45:37.671
Tama si Su Jin,

440
00:45:37.671 --> 00:45:40.125
Siguro nilalamig ako.

441
00:45:44.246 --> 00:45:47.559
Unang araw ng pag-uwi ni Jun Seo
pagkatapos ipanganak,

442
00:45:48.200 --> 00:45:52.419
Hindi mo maiwasang tumingin sa kanya.

443
00:45:54.445 --> 00:45:57.245
Hindi mo naaalala, di ba?

444
00:45:59.652 --> 00:46:03.365
<i>Tinanong kita kung bakit.</i>

445
00:46:04.049 --> 00:46:06.238
<i>Dahil ito ay kaibig-ibig.</i>

446
00:46:06.238 --> 00:46:07.696
<i>Pagkatapos,</i>

447
00:46:07.696 --> 00:46:09.585
<i>hawakan ito</i>

448
00:46:09.585 --> 00:46:12.885
<i>dahan-dahan, ganito.</i>

449
00:46:14.183 --> 00:46:17.316
<i>At alam mo ba kung ano ang ginawa mo?</i>

450
00:46:28.678 --> 00:46:31.495
<i>Sabi mo malamig ang mga kamay mo,</i>

451
00:46:31.495 --> 00:46:35.575
<i>maaari mong bigyan ng sipon ang sanggol.</i>

452
00:46:42.189 --> 00:46:43.752
Jun Kyung,

453
00:46:44.822 --> 00:46:46.972
ikaw ay isang mainit na tao.

454
00:46:51.238 --> 00:46:54.012
- Oh talaga?
- Oo naman.

455
00:49:24.405 --> 00:49:26.283
dumating ako.

456
00:49:26.283 --> 00:49:28.229
Nakatira ka ba sa bahay ng isang kaibigan?

457
00:49:28.229 --> 00:49:30.689
Maaari kang sumulat man lang sa akin.

458
00:49:31.342 --> 00:49:33.202
Teka.

459
00:49:33.202 --> 00:49:35.135
Anong nangyari sa mukha mo?

460
00:49:35.135 --> 00:49:36.996
nahulog ako.

461
00:49:36.996 --> 00:49:38.466
uminom ka ba

462
00:49:38.466 --> 00:49:40.062
Hindi.

463
00:49:40.895 --> 00:49:44.228
Tumatakbo ako pababa ng hagdan ng subway.

464
00:49:44.228 --> 00:49:46.890
Dapat naging mas maingat ka.

465
00:49:46.890 --> 00:49:50.284
Nilagyan ko na ng ointment, wala lang.

466
00:49:50.284 --> 00:49:52.595
- Diyos...
- Huwag hawakan.

467
00:49:52.595 --> 00:49:54.370
Mukhang masakit.

468
00:49:55.301 --> 00:49:57.914
Bakit bigla kang naglaba ng damit ni nanay?

469
00:50:01.412 --> 00:50:03.338
Well, maganda ang panahon.

470
00:50:19.432 --> 00:50:21.051
Jun Seo,

471
00:50:22.346 --> 00:50:24.519
Paano kung puntahan natin si mama?

472
00:51:45.165 --> 00:51:47.171
- Tatay.
- Oo?

473
00:51:54.060 --> 00:51:55.886
salamat po.

474
00:52:11.432 --> 00:52:14.765
Nasobrahan yata ako noong araw na iyon.

475
00:52:20.674 --> 00:52:22.074
Hindi.

476
00:52:24.520 --> 00:52:26.727
Dahil sa naramdaman mo,

477
00:52:26.727 --> 00:52:29.000
Ito ay naiintindihan.

478
00:52:34.861 --> 00:52:37.261
Anyway...

479
00:52:42.355 --> 00:52:44.194
pasensya na po.

480
00:52:58.482 --> 00:53:00.575
Alam din ba ito ni Jun Seo?

481
00:53:05.461 --> 00:53:07.874
Pag nalaman niya, mababaliw siya diba?

482
00:53:08.575 --> 00:53:11.362
Kilala siya, malamang.

483
00:53:11.362 --> 00:53:15.574
Dapat mong piliin ang tamang sandali.

484
00:53:17.073 --> 00:53:18.473
Ang sandali.

485
00:53:24.800 --> 00:53:28.286
Malamang good mood siya ngayon.

486
00:53:28.286 --> 00:53:30.706
May magandang nangyayari ba sa iyo?

487
00:53:39.464 --> 00:53:41.151
<i>Ako...</i>

488
00:53:42.325 --> 00:53:44.437
<i>Mahal kita.</i>

489
00:54:00.423 --> 00:54:02.909
Mag-internship ka diba?

490
00:54:04.003 --> 00:54:05.543
Oo.

491
00:54:06.817 --> 00:54:08.433
Nagyabang ako ng kaunti.

492
00:54:08.433 --> 00:54:11.306
Sabi ko tinalo mo sila
sa ilang graduate students.

493
00:54:11.920 --> 00:54:14.086
Binabati kita.

494
00:54:14.713 --> 00:54:17.173
Hoy, kumain ka na.

495
00:54:29.165 --> 00:54:31.231
Sa katunayan,

496
00:54:31.231 --> 00:54:33.077
Nag-resign ako.

497
00:54:34.984 --> 00:54:36.731
- Iyon?
- Dahil?

498
00:54:38.807 --> 00:54:40.442
hindi ko alam.

499
00:54:40.442 --> 00:54:42.368
Nangyari lang.

500
00:54:42.952 --> 00:54:46.184
- Dahil...?
- Bakit mo binigay iyon?

501
00:54:47.265 --> 00:54:49.138
Dahil?

502
00:54:51.198 --> 00:54:53.424
Dahil nakipaghiwalay ako kay Sol.

503
00:54:54.732 --> 00:54:56.231
ano?

504
00:55:02.760 --> 00:55:04.974
I'm sorry, dad.

505
00:55:04.974 --> 00:55:07.354
Alam kong napakasaya mo noon.

506
00:55:07.354 --> 00:55:08.804
Hindi, hindi iyon...

507
00:55:08.804 --> 00:55:10.957
Nag-resign ka ba dahil...?

508
00:55:23.870 --> 00:55:26.276
Siguradong marami kang pinaghirapan.

509
00:55:30.313 --> 00:55:32.037
Bakit ka tumigil sa pagsasalita?

510
00:55:32.037 --> 00:55:34.437
Pagalitan mo ako as always.

511
00:55:35.340 --> 00:55:38.260
Deserve ko to.

512
00:55:39.280 --> 00:55:41.400
Sige.

513
00:55:41.400 --> 00:55:42.838
Ang mahalaga

514
00:55:42.838 --> 00:55:45.380
Kaya mo lang nakuha ang internship na iyon nang mag-isa.

515
00:55:48.642 --> 00:55:50.252
Anong kaluwagan.

516
00:55:50.252 --> 00:55:53.785
Hindi ko alam kung paano ko sasabihin.

517
00:56:04.646 --> 00:56:06.337
Miss ko na si Bom.

518
00:56:06.337 --> 00:56:08.627
Naglalakbay ba muli ang iyong kaibigan?

519
00:56:08.627 --> 00:56:10.503
Dalhin mo si Bom minsan.

520
00:56:11.756 --> 00:56:13.339
Sino si Bom?

521
00:56:13.339 --> 00:56:15.155
Aso ng kaibigan ni Tatay.

522
00:56:17.634 --> 00:56:19.031
Sa katunayan,

523
00:56:19.031 --> 00:56:21.607
Si Bom ay hindi aso ng kaibigan.

524
00:56:22.234 --> 00:56:23.740
yun?

525
00:56:26.780 --> 00:56:29.366
Aso ito ng girlfriend ko.

526
00:56:32.377 --> 00:56:33.983
yun?

527
00:56:45.095 --> 00:56:47.694
Halos dalawang buwan na tayong magkasama,

528
00:56:48.462 --> 00:56:52.162
at halos tatlong buwan na kaming magkakilala.

529
00:56:54.002 --> 00:56:56.096
Nangyari lang.

530
00:56:56.096 --> 00:56:59.100
Nagmahalan kami...

531
00:56:59.100 --> 00:57:00.689
tatay,

532
00:57:00.689 --> 00:57:03.722
Hindi mo kailangang pumunta sa mga detalye.

533
00:57:07.150 --> 00:57:08.234
Teka.

534
00:57:08.234 --> 00:57:10.821
Ang kanilang mga kuwento ay magkatulad.

535
00:57:10.821 --> 00:57:12.858
Kamusta ang katabi?

536
00:57:12.858 --> 00:57:15.837
Oo, kumusta ang mga bagay sa lalaking iyon?

537
00:57:21.574 --> 00:57:23.133
anong nangyayari?

538
00:57:24.187 --> 00:57:26.420
Iniwan ka na ba niya?

539
00:57:26.420 --> 00:57:28.193
Well...

540
00:57:30.680 --> 00:57:34.126
sa totoo lang...siya...

541
00:57:36.167 --> 00:57:37.597
may anak na lalaki

542
00:57:37.597 --> 00:57:39.987
15 taong gulang.

543
00:57:39.987 --> 00:57:41.474
- Iyon?
- Iyon?

544
00:57:41.474 --> 00:57:43.546
Hoy, mag-ingat ka!

545
00:57:49.389 --> 00:57:50.980
Wag kang gumalaw.

546
00:57:50.980 --> 00:57:53.015
Manahimik ka.

547
00:57:57.026 --> 00:57:59.445
So nakikipag-date ka ba sa lalaking may asawa?

548
00:57:59.445 --> 00:58:01.272
baliw ka? Bakit ako makikipag-date sa lalaking may asawa?

549
00:58:01.272 --> 00:58:02.722
hindi ka kasal?

550
00:58:02.722 --> 00:58:04.580
Salamat sa Diyos.

551
00:58:04.580 --> 00:58:06.459
Ang cute niya, good boy siya.

552
00:58:06.459 --> 00:58:08.331
Mabait?

553
00:58:08.331 --> 00:58:10.187
Anong kaluwagan.

554
00:58:11.484 --> 00:58:13.624
Wag kang gumalaw! Pakiusap!

555
00:58:13.624 --> 00:58:15.341
Huwag huminga.

556
00:58:15.341 --> 00:58:16.864
OK.

557
00:58:18.841 --> 00:58:21.208
Lumapit kami kay mama

558
00:58:21.208 --> 00:58:23.201
at halos nakita na namin ito ng totoo.

559
00:58:23.201 --> 00:58:26.182
- Brat...
- Paumanhin, iyon ay wala sa lugar.

560
00:58:26.182 --> 00:58:27.988
pasensya na po.

561
00:58:28.948 --> 00:58:30.841
Ngunit gawin mo

562
00:58:30.841 --> 00:58:32.715
okay lang ba sila?

563
00:58:32.715 --> 00:58:34.259
Sa tingin ko ayos lang ako.

564
00:58:34.259 --> 00:58:36.652
Ako din.

565
00:58:36.652 --> 00:58:37.716
At ikaw?

566
00:58:37.716 --> 00:58:39.396
ayos lang din ako.

567
00:58:39.396 --> 00:58:41.033
Salamat sa Diyos.

568
00:58:41.033 --> 00:58:43.249
Maayos naman kaming lahat.

569
00:58:43.963 --> 00:58:45.786
ngunit

570
00:58:45.786 --> 00:58:48.039
Tayo ba talaga?

571
00:58:53.326 --> 00:58:55.162
-Uy, Jun Seo.
- Oo?

572
00:58:55.162 --> 00:58:57.689
Lumiko ng kaunti ang manibela sa kaliwa.

573
00:58:58.420 --> 00:59:01.012
Hoy, hindi! Manahimik ka.

574
00:59:39.215 --> 00:59:42.552
<i>Ito ba ay isang pakikipagsapalaran lamang?</i>

575
00:59:42.552 --> 00:59:45.256
<i>Sa tingin ko dapat akong humingi ng tawad.</i>

576
00:59:45.256 --> 00:59:47.089
<i>Kaya ko ang aking nararamdaman.</i>

577
00:59:47.089 --> 00:59:48.876
<i>Wala akong hinihiling sa iyo,</i>

578
00:59:48.876 --> 00:59:51.956
<i>kaya hindi mo na kailangang sabihin pa.</i>

579
00:59:51.956 --> 00:59:54.320
<i>Akala ko nandito lang kami para tumambay.</i>

580
00:59:54.320 --> 00:59:57.686
<i>Hindi ko akalain na pupunta kami para bumili ng lugar.</i>

581
00:59:57.686 --> 01:00:01.063
<i>Bahay na walang may-ari, tanging alaala na lang ang natitira.</i>

582
01:00:01.063 --> 01:00:03.896
<i>Aalisin ko ang bahay na ito.</i>

583
01:00:04.619 --> 01:00:07.419
<i>Maiintindihan naman nila, di ba?</i>

584
01:00:07.419 --> 01:00:08.556
<i>ako</i>

585
01:00:08.556 --> 01:00:10.746
<i>Gusto kong makasama si Daniel.</i>

586
01:00:10.746 --> 01:00:12.223
<i>Bakit?</i>

587
01:00:12.223 --> 01:00:13.546
<i>Sa tingin mo ba ay magiging mahirap ito?</i>

588
01:00:13.546 --> 01:00:15.133
<i>Daniel.</i>

589
01:00:15.133 --> 01:00:17.293
<i>Hindi ko gusto ang babaeng iyon.</i>

590
01:00:17.293 --> 01:00:19.946
<i>Hindi ka ba pwedeng makipaghiwalay sa kanya?</i>

591
01:00:19.946 --> 01:00:21.970
<i>Ngayong tagsibol</i>

592
01:00:21.970 --> 01:00:24.330
<i>lalo na ang pait sa pakiramdam.</i>

593
01:00:24.330 --> 01:00:26.810
<i>Hindi mo ba iniisip na magiging malupit ito?</i>

